  Audit Tablespace          SYSADM_AUDIT_TS Dedicated -- isolated from app data
  Autoextend                ON              Prevents space exhaustion
  Max Tablespace Size       50GB            Cap on disk usage (adjust as needed)
  DDL Policy                ALL USERS       ALTER DROP TRUNCATE -- no exceptions
  DML Policy                Non-app users   INSERT UPDATE DELETE
