  Retention Period          90 days         Adjust per compliance requirements
  Space Warning Threshold   70%             Alert logged to dba_audit_space_alerts
  Emergency Purge Threshold 85%             Auto reduces retention to 30 days
  Monitoring Job Frequency  Every 6 hours   Checks tablespace health

